steps.name: Navigate to new link:
Project name:
When I navigate to menu "Web Editor" with submenu "Web Editor"
When I select screen with name /
When I import page name "DEFAULT" & slug "DEFAULT" in web editor with figma file has path "/assets/figma/import_figma_project_variables.studio"
Then I should see the page in web editor with name "ProjectVariablePage" & slug "/projectvariablepage" display in list "Pages"
When I select screen with name ProjectVariablePage
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I select custom item value "Rectangle1" with index "1"
Then I should see the value of color card with label "Background Color" of header "Background" is equal to "PRIMARY_RED"
When I select custom item value "Rectangle2" with index "1"
Then I should see the value of color card with label "Background Color" of header "Background" is equal to "SECONDARY_STYLE"
When I select custom item value "Rectangle3" with index "1"
Then I should see the value of color card with label "Background Color" of header "Background" is equal to "PRIMARY_HARRY"
When I select custom item value "Rectangle4" with index "1"
Then I should see the value of color card with label "Background Color" of header "Background" is equal to "ERIC"
When I navigate to menu "Web Editor" with submenu "Settings"
When I click general tab label "Project Variables"
Then I should see the Project Variable card with name "PRIMARY_RED" and value "#ab4444"
Then I should see the Project Variable card with name "SECONDARY_STYLE" and value "#d9d9d9"
Then I should see the Project Variable card with name "ERIC" and value "#eee863"
